Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent

Class TabServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>>

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent.TabServiceFluent<T>
public class TabServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>> extends Object
Provides a fluent API for interacting with tab UI components.

This class enables interactions with tab elements, including clicking, checking visibility, validating selection, and enabling or disabling tabs. It integrates seamlessly with UiServiceFluent to support method chaining.
